{"type": "article", "id": 19615, "title": "香水包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-24T07:40:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104212fJ0ixFRHcU8v72uq.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是英国的包装设计公司 Stranger &amp; Stranger 设计的香水，里里外外都流露出了神秘感。最外层的黑色包装纸是用印章封起来的，拆开后是颜色炫丽的方盒子，上面的有非常哥特风格的雕塑图案，与盒子构成奇异的反差。香水瓶非常小巧，瓶身围了一圈字母，像是一组有待破解的密码，容易引起人的好奇和欲望。<a href=\"http://lovelypackage.com/eau-de-stranger/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104210CSWm0D6KGy3FIuwQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.07063197\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104210oDxzgBXSMRf9Qv6L.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.02230483\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104211UNdcEqTXyxeBphjC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.2936803\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104211q8gzuniZEaeh3P4w.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.47026022\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071042114dqFOsplPoD19YWG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.54460967\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}